Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:17.16,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ISEKAI NONBIRI NOUKA 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.21,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TAK SANGGUP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:28.86,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KUPID, RAS MALAIKAT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.52,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,RUTINITAS HARIAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.24,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BATU GOLGO, SETARA 1.000 KEPING EMAS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.24,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MAHAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:46.88,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KALAH, MENANG
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.66,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,JANGAN DIAMBIL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.56,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,AMBIL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:27.67,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,AMBIL, JANGAN DIAMBIL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:05.28,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ISEKAI NONBIRI NOUKA 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.41,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ADIKNYA HAKUREN, DOMIME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.67,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,DORAIMU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.43,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,DOMIME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:10.06,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,SLIME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.42,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,RAIMEREN, DOSS, PUTRA KEDUA: DOMIME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:13.77,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PUTRI KETIGA: SEKIREN, PUTRA PERTAMA: DORAIMU,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.81,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PUTRI KEDUA: SUIREN, PUTRI PERTAMA: HAKUREN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:05.11,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TUNANGANNYA DOMIME, KWON
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:50.95,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,SELANJUTNYA:\NEPISODE 7: TIM PENCARI ONSEN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, Desa Pohon Besar\Ntempat kami tinggal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu Desa Satu, Desa Dua, dan Desa Tiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada di dalam hutan\Nyang disebut Hutan Kematian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat pertama kali dengar namanya,\Naku pikir itu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa hutannya diberi nama\Nseram seperti kematian?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasannya, karena di hutan ini\Nnyaris tak ada burung.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isinya monster dan makhluk buas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terutama Demon Spider yang menguasai\Nhutan ini, musuh alami para burung.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di peta pun, hutan ini dicatat menyeramkan,\Nyang bahkan tak ada suara kicauan burung.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, alasan kenapa aku teringat soal itu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena di depan mataku,\Npara makhluk bersayap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}diikat rapat oleh anak-anaknya Zabuton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan dikalahkan oleh anak-anaknya Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada beberapa malaikat yang tak kukenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka itu Harpy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kades!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tak ada lagi\Nyang bersembunyi lagi di area ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, tapi kenapa mereka\Ndiikat kencang di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka seperti ras Malaikat,\Nkamu kenal mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya ini terjadi beberapa waktu lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah desa baru dibangun, area patroli
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi makin luas\Ndan kekurangan yang bertugas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini terlalu luas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Granmaria pun pergi ke permukiman\Nras Malaikat untuk cari bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu putri kepala ras dengar situasi itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengumpulkan pasukannya,\Ndan datang menyerbu ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian! Mau sampai kapan\Nmembiarkan kami begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia putri kepala mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama dia Kupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya memperlakukan ras Malaikat begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jadi ini cara desa kalian menyambut tamu?\N- Kami akan sambut ramah kalian
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Turunkan aku!\N- kalau datang baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bergerombol begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}wajar kalian dianggap musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak ada niat bermusuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu alasannya, kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini demi menjaga kehormatan ras Malaikat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggota ras Malaikat yang seharusnya\Ndihormati dan dimuliakan manusia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}malah hidup malas-malasan di desa ini\Ndan memuja manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau soal dianggap cara hidup berantakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu tergantung masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sampai melanggar adat,\Nitu penghinaan yang tak bisa dimaafkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adat?\NJadi minum sake itu dilarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sampai mengabaikan\NUjian Calon Suami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku merasa ada kesalahpahaman di sini.\N- Hei, turunkan kami dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Singkatnya, kami, ras Malaikat\N- Hei, turunkan kami dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya terdiri dari perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, agar ras kami tak punah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami harus menerima pria\Ndari ras lain sebagai suami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu,\Nkami tak sembarangan memilih pria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar dapat calon suami yang pantas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia harus ikut adat kami,\Nmelewati ujian berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang dia yakini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Oh, lantas kenapa jadi begini?\N- Kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:05:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena Nona Tia dan kami hidup\Nbersama pria dan tak menjalani adat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi dia marah dan menyerbu ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, harusnya jelaskan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Meski dijelaskan, aku tak yakin dia percaya.\N- Kalian, berhenti mengabaikanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yang lain bisa, tapi dia tipe keras kepala.\N- Kalian ini, ini sudah keterlaluan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sulit dipercaya!\N- Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kubilang barusan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tindakan kalian jelas dianggap\Nsebagai serangan terhadap desa kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa cuma aku yang masih diikat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kami sudah menangkap kalian,\Nkami bebas memperlakukan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu kalau kalian dianggap musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kalian menyesali tindakan,\Nmemperbaiki sikap,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan jadi bawahan Granmaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan memaafkan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bersedia setia pada Nona Granmaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian, kenapa mudah sekali\Nberpihak ke mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Baiklah, para malaikat,\N- Kalian! Tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- bagaimana keputusan kalian?\N- Kenapa jadi begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin mereka masih keberatan\Nmelawan putri kepala ras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, Kupid itu calon kepala ras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk para Harpy, mereka tak keberatan\Npada siapa harus melayani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau mereka mengkhianati Kupid,\Nmeski lolos, ke depannya akan dapat masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, kalau itu alasannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerang desa ini termasuk dosa\Nyang tak bisa dimaafkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalang utamanya, Kupid,\Nakan menerima sepuluh hukuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu hukuman saja sudah mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sampai menerima sepuluh,\Nnasibnya akan sangat menyedihkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau tiap satu dari kalian minta maaf,\Ntiap hukumannya dikurangi satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, kalian ingin\Nmenyelamatkan Kupid, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan kalian juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka, pengikut Kupid\Nternyata gampang menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka cuma butuh alasan\Nagar bisa minta maaf tanpa merasa malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau demi melindungi Nona Kupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian jangan bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah minta maaf,\Nkami sambut mereka sebagai tamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisa satu orang lagi.\NKamu harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya menyerah saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa juga yang mau minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini caramu membujuk Tia\Ndan yang lainnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang kelihatan keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.\NKades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu bersedia\Nmenjalani ujian ras Malaikat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini agar bisa membujuk Kupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kalian sadar juga, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pria lemah itu tak akan bisa melewatinya!\N- Kalau berhasil melewati ujiannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pilihan dia hanya menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan disuruh terbang\Natau mengalahkan monster, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurang lebih begitu,\Ntapi aku yakin Kades pasti bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ujian itu sebenarnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai pingsan\Nkarena terlalu sulit, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian ras Malaikat ada lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku langsung merasa ini akan merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, apa ujiannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama cuma pemanasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian pertama:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan Harta.\NSumbangkan 777 koin emas ke ras Malaikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu mahal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mahal untuk orang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bisa diganti dengan barang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa, tapi aku rasa desa ini tak punya barang\Nyang nilainya sama mahalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini Batu Golgo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sengaja mengambilnya\Ndi gudang dekat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, yang berkilauan ini juga\Nlumayan indah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cukup ambil satu ini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu?\NBerarti ujian pertama selesai, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian kedua: Kecerdasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}20 batu ini akan diambil bergantian,\Nyang terakhir mengambilnya kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap giliran hanya boleh ambil\Nsatu sampai tiga batu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap giliran wajib mengambil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya kamu cukup bingung, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku boleh mulai duluan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini tambah satu batu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku giliran kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konon permainan ini sebenarnya\Nwarisan dari ras Malaikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa pun batu yang diambil lawan,\Nkalau bisa, ambil empat batu tiap giliran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ambil tiga batu di awal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian pasti menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan aku tahu permainan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang mirip dan sadar triknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tahu polanya dan pilih giliran,\Nmustahil akan kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya lanjut ke ujian berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian ketiga: Kekuatan Tempur.\NSekarang mulai serius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, apa kamu takut?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, aku tidak percaya diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aturannya sederhana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal lawan orang\Nyang kami tunjuk dan menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua ujian awal menang karena kebetulan,\Ntapi yang ini rasanya mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa lawannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersiaplah untuk terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawanmu musuh alami ras Malaikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Kejam Terkenal, Putri Vampir, Luu Lulucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saking kagetnya sampai tak bisa bicara, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia itu buronan,\Nmustahil bisa menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya menyerah sekarang\Ndemi kebaikan kita bersama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kupanggil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang aku harus duel denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, menurut dan lihat ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat ke sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian keempat:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan negosiasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawanmu Gate Dragon, Raja Gullguld,\Nyang konon mustahil diajak bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Kades, sedang sibuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku sedang repot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sampai nanti.\NHari ini aku bawa daging langka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Gate Dragon itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang terakhir!\NUjian kelima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harta, kecerdasan, kekuatan,\Nkemampuan negosiasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ujiannya terakhirnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keberuntungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesannya ini terlalu tiba-tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang depan itu sayap,\Nyang belakang pedang dan perisai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lempar koin medali ini, kalau bagian depan\Nyang jatuh, kamu yang menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, akan kucoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian ini mengandalkan keberuntungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada cara lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali, yang jatuh bagian belakang!\NUjianmu gagal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa curangmu kurang jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi aku tak sengaja memantulkannya\Ndan kena tanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kurang beruntung, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Tia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan ini, ujiannya selesai, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu curang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu mau kutanam ke lantai juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah repot-repot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dia melihatku,\Npasti akan makin keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku sengaja tidak datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja kamu tidak kelihatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susah diambil, ini medali berharga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada alasan dia sangat terobsesi\Ndengan ujian itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunya sengaja mempermudah ujian agar bisa\Nmenikah dengan ayahnya yang berbeda status,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Kupid terus dirundung karena hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi itu alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, tadi terlalu terbawa emosi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kami harus\Nmenyambutmu sebagai tamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begitu,\Nkeributan ini akhirnya selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupid dan yang lainnya memutuskan\Ntinggal sementara di Desa Satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat normal, Kupid ternyata cukup tenang,\Nbahkan memberi saran soal keamanan desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yahuy!\N- Kalau sudah minum, dia jadi sangat ceria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama dia menikmatinya,\Nitu bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan kembali ke posisi masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat bantuan para Harpy,\Nbeban patroli udara jadi ringan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, hasil yang didapat bukan itu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya Kades bisa mengembalikan kami\Nke Kupid dan tak membela kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, dia tak melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan, kami dapat pengakuan resmi\Ndari ras Malaikat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai pasangan Kades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sebuah kehormatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isekai Nonbiri Nouka... 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Desa ini sering kali didatangi para naga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, jumlah naga di dunia ini
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jauh lebih banyak dari yang kukira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mohon!\NTolong lindungi aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasi ini sudah parah!\NTolong dengarkan, Mbak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah nyaris tak sanggup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naga yang tak kukenal ini
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata adiknya Hakuren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang pasti paham, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu memang kadang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang itu Doraimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini slime sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya mirip-mirip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga mereka seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Domime anak bungsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya selalu mengabaikan ucapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku hidup ketakutan setiap hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naga juga bisa merasa terancam, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, akan terjadi bencana besar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf baru memperkenalkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Kwon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunangannya Tuan Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, aku Hiraku, kades di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira lawannya sosok mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk sementara, dia bukan musuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa dia setakut ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Tuan Domime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu sedang gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Domime, jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lucu sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sebenarnya\Nsenang bertemu denganku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sedang tak enak badan.\NAh, maaf, sepertinya adikku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia keracunan makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, perutku sakit!\NAku kebanyakan minum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kwon, jangan rundung adikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Hakuren, aku tidak merundungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:17:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru aku yang selalu dirundung\NTuan Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah janji pergi bersama,\Ntapi dia sering membatalkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini dia pura-pura\Ntidak ada saat aku datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejauh apa pun dia kabur atau sembunyi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mustahil aku kehilangan jejak Tuan Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada wanita lain yang kamu sukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau kamu tak mau menikah denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bicara sebentar dengan Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ingin bicara, lakukan di sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini topik antarpria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, serahkan ini padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah berapa kali kamu kabur?\NApa pernah sekali bisa lolos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru bertemu dengannya sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kwon punya aura yang sangat berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak akan bisa kabur darinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada syarat khusus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal menikah dengan Kwon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.\NSebenarnya aku tak mau menikah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerahlah! Begitu kalian bertemu,\Nnasib sudah ditentukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Semangat, semangat!\N- Dia bahkan hadir saat aku lahir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Semangat, semangat!\N- Berarti itu takdir! Terima saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, belum waktunya putus asa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan syarat yang membuatmu\Ntak berat menikahinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada yang membuatmu tidak nyaman\Natau ingin kamu minta dia berhenti, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu diperbaiki, mungkin kamu\Nbisa menerima pernikahan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!\NMustahil dia mau mendengarkanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu pernah menjelaskan\Nperasaanmu padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum pernah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu jangan ragu.\NHadapi dia, jangan kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, bicara langsung padanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tulis di kertas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lewatkan hal sekecil apa pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap makin banyak yang ditulis,\Nmakin besar peluang dia berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sungkan, tulis semuanya sampai kamu\Nmerasa rela menikah dengan Kwon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Domime bilang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum itu, Kwon.\NKamu serius ingin menikah dengan Domime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski harus melewati kesulitan apa pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu diberi tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, Domime sedang menulis surat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menulis semua hal yang dia harapkan\Ndari calon istrinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Calon istrinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu keinginan Tuan Domime,\Naku harus memenuhi semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menduga kamu akan bilang begitu,\Ntapi itu saja tidak cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta itu bukan sepihak\Nharus menuruti yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau menjadi pasutri,\Nperasaan kedua belah pihak harus dihargai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan kedua belah pihak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, kamu juga harus menuliskan\Nkeinginanmu di kertas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tulis apa yang Domime ingin lakukan padamu,\Natau hal yang ingin kamu ubah darinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga menulis hal yang sama,\Njadi tak perlu sungkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begitu, kalian setara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku ingin pinjam ruangan kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malu kalau ini dibaca\Nselain Tuan Domime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini, dia jadi wanita biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita ras Naga itu sulit dihadapi.\NKamu harus bersiap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sedang bahas apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kami tak bahas apa pun!\NSaking tidak penting, kami malah kaget!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kita pergi berkencan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kamu makan bekal buatanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesekali, aku juga ingin\Nbergandengan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jujur saja, aku takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini keinginanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}To-To-Tolong dibaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan ini, hubungan mereka maju selangkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, untuk beberapa waktu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}surat menyurat mereka berlanjut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu dengan menakutkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresimu itu yang membuatku takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu saat akhirnya mereka pulang,\Nkeduanya bisa pulang bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka melakukan hal yang ribet, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang butuh waktu, tapi berkat itu\Nmereka bisa memikirkannya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kamu sangat perhatian\Npada Domime, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibiarkan, mereka akan\Nkejar-kejaran dalam wujud naga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau urusan orang lain kubiarkan,\Ntapi dia sudah seperti keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak bisa kuabaikan begitu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mungkin aku juga\Nharus menulis surat untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kamu minta apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, itu rahasia\Nsampai kamu membacanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan terlalu kasar.
